Titolo: Katamari Amore

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: Katamari Amore (塊魂 アモーレ, Katamari Amore) was a third-person puzzle-action video game that is published and developed by Namco Bandai Games for iOS. With rumors beginning in March 2011, the game was revealed in a pre-release state at E3 2011, and was released to the public on September 29. Katamari Amore is the second game of the Katamari franchise to be released on iOS, and features Game Center integration.
The game's plot revolves around the main character Prince retrieving specific items on the planet Earth for his father the King of All Cosmos.
Katamari Amore was removed from the Apple Store on March 30, 2015.